    "description": "Join tournament here https://lichess.org/tournament/QGwrRRTF\nSearch all my videos easy https://agadmator-library.github.io/\n\nAnand, Viswanathan (2743) - Firouzja, Alireza (2762)\nTech Mahindra Global Chess League (Chess.com) [25] 2025.12.21\nB51 Sicilian, Canal-Sokolsky (Nimzovich-Rossolimo, Moscow) attack\n\n1.e4 c5 2.Nf3 d6 3.Bb5+ Nd7 4.O-O a6 5.Bxd7+ Bxd7 6.c3 Nf6 7.Re1 Bg4 8.h3 Bh5 9.d4 cxd4 10.cxd4 e6 11.d5 e5 12.Qb3 Be7 13.Nfd2 Nd7 14.Nc3 b5 15.Nf1 Nc5 16.Qc2 Rc8 17.a3 O-O 18.Be3 Bg6 19.Ng3 Qd7 20.f3 a5 21.Qd1 Bh4 22.Bf2 a4 23.Rb1 Nb3 24.Qd3 Rc4 25.Rbd1 Rfc8 26.Rf1 h6 27.Nge2 Nc5 28.Qd2 Bd8 29.Nc1 Ba5 30.N1a2 f5 31.exf5 Bxf5 32.Qe2 Nb3 33.Be3 Nd4 34.Qf2 Nc2 35.Bb6 Bxb6 36.Qxb6 Nd4 37.Nb4 Bxh3 38.Nc6 Nxc6 39.dxc6 R8xc6 40.Qb8+ Kh7 41.gxh3 Qxh3 42.Rd2 b4 43.axb4 a3 44.b5 Rc8 45.Qxd6 axb2 46.Qd3+ Kh8 47.Ne4 Rb4 48.Qb1 Qxf1+\n\n0:01 Hello Everyone!\n00:40 Game Starts!\n01:41 Completely new game\n08:20 Pause the Video!\n13:15 Pause the Video 2\n13:25 It Was in This Position\n14:45 Legends of The Channel\n\nCheck out agadmator's merch here https://teespring.com/stores/agadmators-swag-store\nhttps://teespring.com/design-with-a-story-tm\n\nMailbox where you can send stuff:\n\nAntonio Radić\nAGADMATOR d.o.o.\nFranje Tuđmana 12\nCroatia\n48260 Križevci \np.s. this is not my home address :)\n\nContact me: agadmator@gmail.com \n\nVideo created by OBS\n\n----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------\nIf you realllly enjoy my content, you're welcome to support me and my channel with a small donation via PayPal or Crypto.\n\nLink to PayPal donation https://www.paypal.me/agadmator\n\nMaiar Wallet @agadmator or join me here https://get.maiar.com/referral/pv0mam6l2a\nBTC address bc1qckd3ut0hqyymzv33eus97ld8klj02xhk2kcwld\nBCH address qzmfclyn69hqhjslls40r7r0dsttwe3tcsl946w4fr\nLTC address Laarf1RmvCpLt2BcSwC1PBLG3hRC4HjBrz\nNANO nano_1h1kgfaq88t1btwadqzx73rbha5hwbb8